body:
This PR will remove unnecessary zeros from input of $logic_not.

```
module test(input [7:0] a, input [7:0] b, output [7:0] y);
  assign y = !{({a, 4'b0000}+1), 1'b0, ({b, 4'b0000} + 1'b1)};
endmodule
```

